We were upgraded to a partial ocean view suite and the room was clean and comfortable.	The room was spacious and had really cool furnishings, and the beds were comfortable.	The staff were helpful and moved us to a much larger room with a safe and more modern bathroom.	The room was spacious and very unique - with a massive plasma tv and a bunch of cable channels.	The location is unbeatable - less than a block away from Venice Beach - and the balcony had a great view of the beach (it helped that the weather was great).